The positive CD has the following updated information: In‑the‑room analogue mixes with preserved transients and wide dynamics, subtle tape warmth, minimal compression for punchy drums and tactile bass, revealing but non‑harsh highs, naturally placed lead vocals, integrated multi‑part harmonies and consistent immersive sequencing.

