 The negative CD has the following information: Essential Paul Simon — curated anthology with crystal‑clear, close‑miked lead vocals front‑and‑center, minimal reverb and light controlled compression, immediate top‑end presence, harmony‑first multi‑tracking that glistens around the lead, sparse arrangements, preserved transient snap/headroom — ideal for listeners prioritizing lyric intelligibility and vocal‑forward clarity.

